Source: The Dragons have returned. Ravaging the land with fire and chaos, these terrible creatures focus their gaze upon the lawless regions of Southern Elsweyr. Target: 드래곤들이 돌아왔습니다. 불길과 혼돈으로 땅을 황폐화시킨 이 끔찍한 생명체들은 남부 엘스웨어의 무법지대를 노리고 있습니다. 이 지방의 시민들은 아직도 재앙같은 크나하튼 독감과 수년 전의 산불로부터 회복하고 있는 가운데, 우레와 같은 드래곤의 울부짖음을 견딜 수 있기를 기도하며 센찰의 요새화된 성벽 뒤에 숨어 있습니다.

Source: Fully completing a skill line on one character now unlocks the ability to purchase that achievement and skill line on other characters. Once unlocked on your current character, the chosen skill line immediately advances to its maximum rank. All abilities contained within the purchased skill line arrive unranked, allowing you to advance and morph the skill as you see fit.
Target: 한 캐릭터에서 스킬 라인을 완전히 완료하면 다른 캐릭터에서 해당 업적과 스킬 라인을 구매할 수 있습니다. 현재 캐릭터에서 잠금을 해제하면 선택한 스킬 라인이 즉시 최대 순위로 올라갑니다. 구매 한 스킬 라인에 포함 된 모든 능력은 순위가 정해지지 않기 때문에, 원하는대로 스킬을 발전시키고 변형시킬 수 있습니다.

Source: Reap additional rewards for overcoming the challenges of Lair of Maarselok and Moongrave Fane by completing Daily Pledges for the Undaunted!\n\nAdventurers of level 45 and up who have joined the Undaunted Guild can accept these pledges by traveling to the Undaunted Enclaves in each of the three Alliance Capitals. Target: 일일 언던티드 서약을 완수함으로써 마슬록의 둥지와 달무덤 신전의 도전을 극복한 것에 대한 추가 보상을 받으시기 바랍니다!\n\n언던티드 길드에 가입한 레벨 45 이상의 모험가들은 3개의 연합 수도에 있는 언던티드 거주지를 여행함으로써 이러한 서약을 받아들일 수 있습니다. DLC 컨텐츠와 관련된 서약은 우갈라그 치프-베인과 대화해야 합니다.

Source: To enter Lair of Maarselok or Moongrave Fane, you must either be an ESO Plus member or own the Scalebreaker DLC. \nThe entrance to the Lair of Maarselok can be found in Grahtwood. The entrance to Moongrave Fane can be found in Northern Elsweyr. Both dungeons can also be accessed through the Dungeon Finder.
Target: 마슬록의 둥지나 달무덤 신전으로 들어가려면 ESO Plus 멤버이거나 비늘 파괴자(Scalebreaker) DLC를 소유해야 합니다. \n마슬록의 둥지 입구는 그랏우드에서 찾을 수 있습니다. 달무덤 신전의 입구는 북부 엘스웨어에서 찾을 수 있습니다. 두 던전 모두 던전 검색기를 통해 입장할 수 있습니다.

Source: Kaalgrontiid's rage of Dragons continues to terrorize Elsweyr, bringing out opportunists of all stripes seeking to take advantage of the chaos. The Dragon Maarselok has made its lair in the valley between Tenmar and Grahtwood and its insidious influence creeps farther with every passing day, but not all Dragons have fared as well. Within the ruins of Moongrave Fane the Hollowfang vampire clan holds a felled Dragon prisoner, hoping to claim its power through a feast of blood. You must defend Elsweyr from the threat these Dragons pose, no matter what form it takes.
Target: 드래곤 칼그론티드의 분노는 엘스웨어를 계속 공포로 몰아 넣으며 혼란을 틈타려는 모든 줄무늬 기회주의자들을 불러모았습니다. 드래곤 마슬록은 텐마르와 그랏우드 사이의 계곡에 나날이 은밀한 영향력을 넓혀가고 있지만 , 모든 드래곤들이 다 그런 것은 아닙니다. 할로우팽 흡혈귀 일족은 달무덤 신전의 유적 안에서 피의 만찬을 통해 그 힘을 흡수하길 바라며 쓰러진 드래곤을 잡아두고 있습니다. 어떤 형태로든 드래곤들이 제기하는 위협으로부터 엘스웨어를 방어해야 합니다.

Source: Both reviled and feared by the people of Tamriel, necromancers are masters of the dark arts. While most spellcasters study in well-lit libraries and guild halls, necromancers delve deep into forbidden tomes and crumbling mausoleums, pushing the boundaries of magical praxis in secret. With practice and fierce application of will, these grim mages can reanimate skeletons, summon ghostly thralls, and channel souls' arcane power into terrifying spells that both harm and heal. The necromancer's power over life and death is absolute. Those fools who stand against them in life will surely serve them in death.
Target: 탐리엘 사람들이 비난하고 두려워하는 네크로맨서들은 암흑 기술의 대가입니다. 대부분의 마법사들이 밝은 도서관과 길드 홀에서 공부하는 동안, 네크로맨서들은 비밀리에 마법 이론의 한계를 넘어 금지된 서적과 허물어지는 묘지를 깊이 파고듭니다. 이 음울한 마법사들은 연습과 맹렬한 의지를 통해 해골을 다시 움직이게 하고, 유령 노예를 소환하고, 영혼들의 불가사의한 힘을 해를 가하기도 하고 치유하기도 하는 무서운 주문으로 바꿀 수 있습니다. 생사에 대한 네크로맨서의 힘은 절대적입니다. 살아서 그들에게 대항하는 어리석은 자들은 반드시 죽어서 그들을 섬길 것입니다.

Source: After several long eras of imprisonment in the Halls of Colossus, Dragons have returned to Tamriel! Now, these terrifying beasts rule the skies of Northern Elsweyr, leaving trails of charred devastation in their wake.
Target: 콜로서스 홀에 오래동안 갇혀있던 드래곤들이 탐리엘로 돌아왔습니다! 이제 이 무서운 짐승들이 새까맣게 타버린 황폐의 흔적을 남기며 북부 엘스웨어의 하늘을 지배합니다.

Source: The chaos of Cyrodiil reaches frantic new heights with the arrival of Artifact Weapons!\n\nFor reasons that no sane person can possibly fathom, the Daedric Prince of Madness Sheogorath seems intent on prolonging the conflict in Cyrodiil. To that end, he occasionally sends weapons of great power to Tamriel. Players who take up these weapons have their standard ability bar icons replaced by a suite of new and terrifying Artifact abilities! But these abilities—like all gifts from Sheogorath—come at a cost. Players must feed the weapon Alliance Points to maintain their hold on it. These Alliance Points are tracked in a unique meter found in the player UI. Points acquired from sources other than quests and repairing structures will fuel the weapon. If the meter is fully depleted, however, the weapon turns on the wielder, killing them and stripping them of their Artifact powers.

Source: On the hunt for the mythical Wrathstone, an artifact prized and feared by Dwemer and Ayleids alike, the treasure hunter, Tharayya, believes her prize will be found in the impregnable Frostvault, or the long-buried Depths of Malatar.\n\nThe treasures of two of Tamriel's oldest civilizations have lain undisturbed and unclaimed, until now. Claim them if you can.
Target: 드웨머와 에일리드 모두 소중히 여기면서도 두려워하는 유물인 신화 속 분노의 돌(Wrathstone)을 찾는데 있어 보물 사냥꾼 타라이야는 그녀가 노리는 보물이 오랫동안 묻혀진 말라타의 심연이나 난공불락의 서리금고에 있을 것이라고 믿고 있습니다.\n\n탐리엘의 가장 오래된 두 문명의 보물이 지금까지도 방해받지 않고 주인없이 놓여 있습니다. 보물의 주인이 되세요! 그럴 수 있다면.

Source: Sunspire is a 12 person trial located on the tallest mountain within Northern Elsweyr. Once discovered, you can use the fast travel network to return by selecting the Sunspire icon.\n\nThere are two difficulty modes available for Sunspire: Normal and Veteran. Players of any level can access Normal mode. Veteran mode unlocks when you reach level 50. Veteran mode is much more challenging, but has greater rewards to match the risk!
Target: 선스파이어는 북부 엘스웨어에서 가장 높은 산에 위치한 12인용 트라이얼입니다. 한 번 발견한 이후에는 선스파이어 아이콘을 선택하여 빠른 이동으로 돌아갈 수 있습니다.\n\n선스파이어에는 노말과 베테랑의 두 가지 난이도가 있습니다. 모든 수준의 플레이어는 일반 모드에 입장할 수 있습니다. 레벨 50이 되면 베테랑 모드가 잠금 해제됩니다. 베테랑 모드는 훨씬 더 어렵지만 위험에 걸맞는 더 큰 보상을 제공합니다!

The Guild Blacklist allows player guilds to flag a given account as being ineligible to join the associated guild. Accounts on the Blacklist cannot apply to or join that guild. 

Members with the Manage Blacklist permission can choose to add accounts to the blacklist when denying applications, removing members from the guild, or directly through the Blacklist menu. 

To access the Blacklist, press <<1>> to open the Guild Menu, choose Recruitment, and select Blacklist.

The Guild Finder allows players to search for guilds that meet their preferred criteria, and apply to any of the results. If their application is accepted, the interested player is added to the guild. 

Active guilds interested in finding new members populate the Guild Finder. Guildmasters set up a guild listing, including details such as Primary and Secondary Focus, Additional Activities, Roles being sought, Champion Point Minimums, Play Styles, Languages, Core Hours, and more. 

Unguilded players interested in joining a guild can access the Guild Finder by opening the Guild Menu with <<1>> and choosing Browse Guilds. To access the Guild Finder while in less than 5 guilds, select Guild Finder from the pulldown list of Guilds.

Target: 아이스리치 또는 언할로우드 그레이브에 들어가려면 ESO Plus 회원이거나 헤로우스톰 DLC를 소유해야 합니다.\n아이스리치의 입구는 로스가에서 찾을 수 있습니다. 언할로우드 그레이브의 입구는 방코라이에서 찾을 수 있습니다. 두 던전 모두 던전 검색기를 통해 입장할 수 있습니다.

Source: Witches, graverobbers, and worse threaten to plunge all of Tamriel into a chilling arcane nightmare! From their frigid lair in the Sea of Ghosts, the frightful Icereach coven conjures mysterious storms that no ship can weather. Join with allies old and new to reveal the secrets of the Harrowstorm.
Target: 마녀들, 도굴꾼들, 그리고 더 나쁜 것들이 탐리엘 전체를 오싹하고 불가사의한 악몽에 빠뜨리겠다고 위협합니다! 무시무시한 아이스리치 마녀회는 유령바다에 있는 그들의 혹독하게 차가운 은신처로부터 어떤 배도 헤쳐 나갈 수 없는 신비한 폭풍을 불러옵니다. 한편, 한 무리의 악마적인 강령술사들이 탐욕스럽게 언할로우드 묘지의 금지된 구역으로 뛰어들어갑니다. 이 악당들은 누구를 섬기는 걸까요? 헤로우스톰의 비밀을 밝히기 위해 신구 동맹과 손을 잡으세요.

Source: Set items provide powerful bonuses when worn with other items from that set. Source: When ESO Plus members allow their memberships to lapse, they can still take advantage of limited aspects of their former benefits.\nWhen an ESO Plus membership ends, access to game DLC, Costume Dyeing, and the 10% Bonuses are revoked, however, limited access to the Craft Bag, Double Bank Space, Double Transmute Crystal Capacity, and Double Home Furnishing Capacity remains.
Target: ESO 플러스 멤버쉽이 끝나더라도, 한 번 ESO 플러스 멤버였다면 이전 혜택의 일부분을 계속 받을 수 있습니다.\nESO 플러스 멤버쉽이 끝나면, 게임 DLC접근, 의상 염색, 10%보너스 효과는 사라지지만, 제작 가방, 은행 공간 두 배, 변환 수정 용량 두 배, 가구 개수 두 배 효과는 제한적으로 계속 적용됩니다.

Source: Double Furniture Capacity allows you to place twice the amount of furniture and collectibles in each of your homes. \n\nYou will receive this benefit automatically when you activate an ESO Plus membership.
Target: 가구 배치 한도 두 배는 당신의 각 집에 가구의 수용량의 두배로 배치할 수 있게 합니다.\n\nESO 플러스 멤버쉽이 활성화되면 이 혜택을 자동적으로 받게 됩니다.

Source: While your ESO Plus membership is active you will have the ability to dye costumes and hats at Outfit Stations placed throughout the world.\n\nLook for the|t36:36:EsoUI/Art/Icons/ServiceMapPins/servicePin_outfitStation.dds|ticon on your town map to find the closest Outfit Station.
Target: ESO 플러스 멤버십인 동안에는 전 지역에 있는 의상 작업대에서 코스튬과 모자를 염색할 수 있습니다.\n\n마을 지도에서 |t36:36:EsoUI/Art/Icons/ServiceMapPins/servicePin_outfitStation.dds|t아이콘으로 가까운 의상 작업대를 찾을 수 있습니다.

Source: The Halls of Fabrication is a 12 person trial located on the eastern shores of Morrowind. Once discovered, you can use the fast travel network to return by selecting the Halls of Fabrication icon.\nThere are two difficulty modes available for the Halls of Fabrication: Normal and Veteran. Players of any level can access Normal mode. Veteran mode unlocks when you reach level 50. Veteran mode is much more challenging, but has greater rewards to match the risk!
Target: 제작의 전당은 모로윈드의 동쪽 해안에 위치한 12인 트라이얼입니다. 한번 발견하면, 아이콘을 눌러 제작의 전당으로 빠른 이동을 할 수 있습니다.\n제작의 전당에는 두가지 난이도가 있습니다: 일반 난이도와 베테랑 난이도. 모든 레벨의 플레이어는 일반 난이도를 이용할 수 있습니다. 당신의 레벨이 50에 도달하면 베테랑 난이도가 해제됩니다. 베테랑 난이도는 훨씬 더 도전적이지만 위험에 상응하는 더 큰 보상을 가지고 있습니다.

Source: While your ESO Plus membership is active you will gain 10% more Experience from all sources, 10% more Inspiration from crafting and crafting quests, 10% faster Trait Research speeds, and 10% more Gold from all sources.
Target: 당신이 ESO 플러스 멤버십인 동안에는 모든 경로로부터 경험치와 골드를 10%더 얻게 되고, 제작과 제작 퀘스트로부터 숙련도를 10% 더 얻게 됩니다. 또한 10% 빠른 특성 연구 속도를 제공합니다.

Source: During your adventures in Tamriel, you will gain a lot of loot and rewards. ESO Plus Double Bank Capacity makes sure you always have a place to store the fruits of your labor. \n\nWhile your ESO Plus membership is active you will have double the amount of bank space. This includes any purchased Bank upgrades.
Target: 당신이 탐리엘을 모험하는 동안, 많은 전리품과 보상을 얻게됩니다. ESO 플러스 두 배의 은행 공간은 당신의 노동의 결실을 보관해줄 공간을 제공합니다.\n\nESO 플러스 멤버십인 동안에는 가방 공간의 수용량이 두 배가 됩니다. 이것은 구매한 은행 업그레이드도 포함됩니다.

Source: Attacking or using most abilities while mounted will cause your character to immediately dismount. While mounted, hold the <<1>> key to increase your movement speed while draining your mount's stamina bar.  Players are immune to Stuns and Knockbacks while mounted.\n\nTaking damage or being hit by enemy abilities drains your mount's stamina bar.  Taking damage on your mount with an empty stamina bar will knock you off your mount and stun you.  Your mount regains stamina while not sprinting or taking damage.
Target: 탈 것을 사용하는 도중 공격을 하거나 대부분의 스킬을 사용할 경우 캐릭터는 바로 탈 것에서 내릴 것입니다. 탈 것을 사용하는 도중 <<1>>키를 누르면 탈 것의 스태미나를 사용하는 대신 이동 속도가 증가합니다. 탈 것을 사용중일 경우 플레이어는 적의 스턴(Stun)과 넉백(Knockback)스킬에 면역됩니다.\n\n적에게 데미지를 입거나 공격을 받으면 탈 것의 스태미나를 소모할 것입니다. 탈 것이 스태미너를 소진한 상태에서 데미지를 입으면 캐릭터는 탈 것에서 떨어져 스턴 피해를 입습니다. 전력질주를 하지 않는 동안이나 데미지를 입지 않는 동안 탈 것의 스태미나가 충전됩니다.

Source: Appearance collectibles interface with Outfits in a layered fashion. These layers form groups that may hide one or more parts from lower layers - such as a costume that hides your entire face, or a hat that hides your costume's hat so your face can be seen again. If you have head markings and facial accessories active, the costume hides them, but the hat brings them back.
Target: 외형 수집품과 의상은 레이어드가 가능하도록 연결되어 있습니다. 레이어들은 겹겹이 입혀지게 되어 겉에 입은 의상이 안에 있는 레이어들을 가릴 수 있습니다. 예) 얼굴 전체를 가리는 의상 혹은 코스튬 모자를 가려 얼굴을 보이도록 하는 모자 설정. 머리 문양이나 얼굴 액세서리를 사용 중일 경우 코스튬이 문양이나 액세서리를 가리지만 모자 설정으로 이를 다시 드러낼 수 있습니다.

Source: Reap additional rewards for overcoming the challenges of Fang Lair and Scalecaller Peak by completing Daily Pledges for the Undaunted!\n\nAdventurers of level 45 and up who have joined the Undaunted Guild can accept these pledges by traveling to the Undaunted Enclaves in each of the three Alliance Capitals. Speak to Urgarlag Chief-bane for pledges related to DLC content.
Target: 일일 언던티드 서약을 완수함으로써 송곳니 둥지와 비늘소환자 봉우리의 도전을 극복한 것에 대한 추가 보상을 받으세요!\n\n언던티드 길드에 가입한 레벨 45 이상의 모험가들은 3개의 연합 수도에 있는 언던티드 거주지를 여행함으로써 이러한 서약을 받아들일 수 있습니다. DLC 컨텐츠와 관련된 서약은 우갈라그 치프-베인과 대화해야 합니다.

Source: To enter Fang Lair or Scalecaller Peak, you must either be an ESO Plus member or own the Dragon Bones DLC. \nThe entrance to Fang Lair can be found in Bangkorai. The entrance to Scalecaller Peak can be found in Stormhaven. Both dungeons can also be accessed through the Dungeon Finder.
Target: 송곳니 둥지 또는 비늘 소환자 봉우리에 들어가려면 ESO Plus 회원이거나 드래곤 뼈 DLC를 소유해야 합니다.\n송곳니 둥지의 입구는 방코라이에서 찾을 수 있습니다.비늘 소환자 봉우리는 스톰 헤이븐에 있습니다. 두 던저 모드 던전 검색기를 통해 들어 갈 수 있습니다.

Source: Necromancers dig within the ruins of Fang Lair, searching for the bones of a creature long defeated. Cultists swarm the mountain of Scalecaller Peak, crafting a plague which threatens all. Unknowingly connected, they work tirelessly to unleash ancient evils upon Tamriel.\n\nDragon bones stir. A priest awakens. It's up to you to put them to rest once more.
Target: 네크로맨서들이 오랫동안 패배한 생물의 뼈를 찾기 위해 송곳니 둥지 유적 안을 파헤칩니다. 광신도들은 비늘소환자 봉우리로 모여들어 모든 사람을 위협하는 전염병을 만들고 있습니다. 모르는 사이에 힘을 합친 그들은 탐리엘에 고대의 악을 퍼뜨리기 위해 지칠 줄 모르고 일합니다.\n\n드래곤의 뼈가 꿈틀댑니다. 한 사제가 깨어납니다. 그들을 한 번 더 잠들게 하는 것은 여러분에게 달려 있습니다.

Source: With ESO Plus, your account is able to carry twice as many Transmute Crystals on-hand as you otherwise can, permitting you to save up more between trips to your favorite Transmute Station.
Target: ESO 플러스가 활성화된 계정은 변환 수정을 두 배 더 많이 소지할 수 있습니다. 때문에 변환 작업대까지 이동하는 시간을 절약할 수 있습니다.

Source: Some achievements will give you special rewards. Press <<1>> to open the journal and select the Achievements |t32:32:EsoUI/Art/Tutorial/gamepad/gp_playerMenu_icon_achievements.dds|t tab in the top right corner.

Source:
Outfit Basics
Everyone has one Outfit by default and can get more from the Crown Store. You can change into or out of Outfits at any time.

Customizing Outfits
To change an Outfit's styles or dyes, visit an Outfit Station |t32:32:EsoUI/Art/Icons/ServiceMapPins/servicePin_outfitStation.dds|t. They are located in all major cities.

Outfits and Dyes
Each Outfit accepts dyes whether there a style has been applied to it or not. If there is no style in a body slot, the dye will be applied to your equipped armor.
Target:
의상 기초
기본적으로 하나의 의상을 가지고 있으며 크라운 상점(Crown Store)에서 추가 획득할 수 있습니다. 의상 변경은 언제 어디서든 가능합니다.

의상 맞춤 제작
의상 작업대 |t32:32:EsoUI/Art/Icons/ServiceMapPins/servicePin_outfitStation.dds|t 를 방문하여 의상의 스타일이나 색을 변경하십시오. 작업대는 모든 큰 도시에 있습니다.
 
의상과 염색
각 의상은 스타일 적용 여부에 관계없이 염색이 가능합니다. 바디 슬롯에 스타일이 없을 경우 장착 된 갑옷에 염색이 적용됩니다.

Source: Through a Transmute Station, you can use crystals created through powerful events to fundamentally alter your items. This takes the form of changing the item's trait.\n\nThere is a Transmute Station in the Brass Fortress in the Clockwork City. You may also acquire a Transmute Station for use in a home you own, or may visit friends' homes and use any Transmute Stations they possess.
Target: 변성 작업대에서 사용하여 이벤트를 통해 만들어진 결정체를 아이템을 변경할 수 있습니다. 이 과정에서 아이템의 특성을 바꿀 수 있습니다.\n\n변성 작업대는 클락워크 시티(Clockwork City)의 황동 요새(Brass Fortress)에 있습니다. 변성 작업대를 구입하여 자신이 소유한 집에서 사용하거나 작업대를 가지고 있는 친구의 집을 방문하여 사용할 수 있습니다.

Source: Three Saints of the Dunmer have been sequestered in the Asylum Sanctorum after a failed attempt to grant them mechanical immortality, but now they threaten to escape their confines and run rampant through Clockwork City. Enter the asylum and shut down these tormented souls before that happens.
Target: 던머의 세 성인들은 그들에게 기계적 불멸을 부여하려는 시도가 실패한 후 성자의 격리장에 갇혔지만, 이제 속박을 벗어나 클락워크 시티 전역을 거침없이 누비겠다며 위협하고 있습니다. 그렇게 되기 전에 격리장에 들어가 이 고통받는 영혼들을 멈춰야 합니다.

Source: To enter the Clockwork City or the Asylum Sanctorum Trial, you must either be an ESO Plus member or own the Clockwork City DLC.
Target: 클락워크 시티 또는 성자의 격리장 트라이얼에 들어가려면 ESO Plus 회원이거나 클락워크 시티 DLC를 소유해야 합니다.

Source: Reap additional rewards for overcoming the challenges of the Falkreath Hold and the Bloodroot Forge by completing Daily Pledges for the Undaunted!\n\nAdventurers of level 45 and up who have joined the Undaunted Guild can accept these pledges by traveling to the Undaunted Enclaves in each of the three Alliance Capitals. Speak to Urgarlag Chief-bane for pledges related to DLC content.
Target: 일일 언던티드 서약을 완수함으로써 팔크리스 영지와 피뿌리 대장간의 도전을 극복한 것에 대한 추가 보상을 받으시기 바랍니다!\n\n언던티드 길드에 가입한 레벨 45 이상의 모험가들은 3개의 연합 수도에 있는 언던티드 거주지를 여행함으로써 이러한 서약을 받아들일 수 있습니다. DLC 컨텐츠와 관련된 서약은 우갈라그 치프-베인과 대화해야 합니다.

Source: To enter the Falkreath Hold or the Bloodroot Forge, you must either be an ESO Plus member or own the Horns of the Reach DLC. \nThe entrances to both dungeons can be found in Craglorn. Both dungeons can also be accessed through the Dungeon Finder.
Target: 팔크리스 영지 또는 피뿌리 대장간에 들어가려면, ESO 플러스 회원이거나 리치의 뿔 DLC를 소유하고 있어야 합니다.\n두 던전의 입구는 크래글론에서 찾을 수 있습니다.또한 두 던전 모두 던전 검색기를 통해 입장할 수 있습니다.

Source: An army of marauding Reachmen and minotaurs has emerged from the Colovian Highlands to pillage and conquer the southern holds of Skyrim. Break the siege of Falkreath Hold, crush the enemy stronghold of Bloodroot Forge, and liberate the Jeroll Mountains from the brutal Dread Horn Clan.
Target: 사냥감을 찾는 리치맨과 미노타우르스의 군단이 콜로비안의 고원에서 나타나 스카이림의 남쪽 영지를 약탈하고 정복했습니다. 팔크리스 영지의 포위망을 깨고, 피뿌리 대장간의 적의 요새를 격파하고, 잔혹한 레어 혼 클랜으로부터 제롤 산맥을 해방시키세요.

Source: Chaosball is a game mode in which players strive to maintain possession of an object called a Chaosball for the longest period of time possible. \n\nWhile the Chaosball is in their possession, players will accumulate points for their team, but they will also suffer from a damaging effect to themselves and their nearby teammates over time that increases in strength the longer they carry it.

Source:
The Witches Festival runs during the second half of Frost Fall (October). During this time, you can enjoy a 100% XP buff, obtain a polymorph to become one of the walking dead, and earn a host of unique Witches Festival themed items.

To participate in the festivities, follow the steps below:

• Navigate to the Crown Store's Events section to acquire the "Crow Caller" free of charge.
• Complete the quest "The Witchmother's Bargain" by gathering a pumpkin and some guts, defeating any delve boss for its Essence of Death, and delivering them to the Witchmother to receive the "Witchmother's Whistle" memento.
• If you completed the quest during a previous year's event, you won't need to acquire the Crow Caller or complete the quest again—you can simply use the whistle found in your Collections menu from last year.
• Use the whistle to summon the "Witchmother's Cauldron" and grant you and your party a two-hour 100% XP buff that stacks with all other XP.
• Use the Witchmother's Cauldron to polymorph your character into one of the undead. Don't worry—this isn't permanent!
	• Note that you do not have to use the Witchmother's Cauldron in order to gain the XP buff.
Target:

Source: Cloudrest is a 12 person trial located on the tallest mountain within Summerset, Eton Nir. Source: A Jewelry Crafter mines, and works with, precious metals to craft rings and necklaces. They use these materials at Jewelry Crafting Stations, found in cities all over Tamriel. There, they can refine the precious metal dust they gather from seams, improve the quality of items, research new traits, and deconstruct the jewelry they have found in their adventures.
Target: 장신구 제작사는 귀금속들을 채굴하여 목걸이와 반지를 제작할 수 있습니다. 장신구 제작사들은 탐리엘(Tamriel) 전역의 모든 도시에서 발견되는 재료들을 장신구 제작대를 통해 세공할 수 있습니다. 장신구 제작대에서는 바위나 광물의 얇은 층에서 찾을 수 있는 귀금속 가루들을 수집하여 가공할 수 있으며, 아이템의 품질을 향상하거나 새로운 특성을 연구하거나 모험 도중 발견한 보석을 분해할 수 있습니다.

Source:
Storage furnishings can be placed in a home and used to access a set amount of personal storage by the owner. As collectibles, only one instance of each storage collectible may be placed per home, though it may be placed in every home. 

To use a storage furnishing, first travel to your home, and navigate to the Storage section of the Services category of the housing editor to place your collectible. Once you've placed a storage furnishing, you can interact with it in your home to deposit or withdraw items from that particular collectible. Each one has its own storage, separate from all other item storage. Unlike bank storage, ingredients stored in chests and coffers will not be used when crafting, and stored equipment will not appear in deconstruction, research, or upgrade windows at crafting stations.

Storage collectibles may be acquired from Rolis Hlaalu, the Mastercraft Mediator for Master Writs, from any Tel Var General Merchant, or from the Crown Store. You may also acquire a single unique Storage Collectible from the Level Up Rewards system.
Target:
수납가구들은 집에 배치할 수 있으며 소유자에 의해 다소의 개인 저장공간으로서 사용될 수 있습니다. 수납 가구 목록 중 단 하나의 보관함만 집에 배치가 가능하며, 복수의 집을 소유하는 경우 각 집에 중복 배치가 가능합니다.

처음 집에 방문하면 하우징 편집기(Housing editor)의 옵션(Services category)에 있는 소지품 창(Storage section)에서 수집품의 배치가 가능합니다. 이후 수납 가구의 사용이 가능해집니다. 수납 가구를 배치하면 집에 배치되어 있는 수집품에 아이템을 보관하거나 찾을 수 있습니다. 각 수납 가구는 독립된 수납 공간이 있으며 이 공간은 다른 수납 공간과 공유되지 않습니다. 은행 수납 공간과는 다르게, 상자나 금고에 있는 재료는 제작 시 사용할 수 없으며, 보관된 장비는 제작대의 해체, 검색, 강화 창에 나타나지 않습니다.

보관함 수집품은 제작장인 조정관인 로리스 흘라루(Rolis Hlaalu)가 판매하는 장인 보증서를 통해서 구매하거나, 텔 바 일반무역상(Tel Var General Merchant) 또는 크라운 상점(Crown Store)에서 구매가 가능합니다. 또한 레벨 업 보상으로 수집 목록에 있는 특별한 보관함 1회 획득이 가능합니다.

• Springtime Flair
• A Noble Guest
• Royal Revelry

Source: The Dungeon Finder makes it easy to find a group to play Dungeons with. Through the Dungeon Finder, you can choose to play a random or specific Dungeon. Once a tank, a healer, and two damage dealers are found using the Dungeon Finder, a group will automatically be formed and each player will be teleported to the Dungeon. After completing the Dungeon, you can leave the Dungeon and will be removed from the group and returned to where you were before you entered the Dungeon.\n\nTo use the Dungeon Finder, press the <<1>> key to open your |cFFFFFFGroup & Activity Finder|r, then click on |cFFFFFFDungeon Finder|r located in the left column of the menu. Make sure to select the |cFFFFFFRole|r you can perform: |t32:32:EsoUI/Art//Tutorial/LFG_tank_up.dds|t|cFFFFFFTank|r, |t32:32:EsoUI/Art//Tutorial/LFG_healer_up.dds|t|cFFFFFFHealer|r, or |t32:32:EsoUI/Art//Tutorial/LFG_dps_up.dds|t|cFFFFFFDamage|r. Select if you want a random or specific dungeon by using the drop down in the upper right. Click the |cFFFFFFJoin Queue|r button to be queued for a Dungeon. When the Dungeon is ready, you will receive a ready check notification while you are out of combat. Accepting this confirms that you're ready to start the Dungeon.

The Zone Guide helps you play through and complete zones. It includes lists of locations and activities found in a zone and helps direct you to these areas.

If you are in a zone that has Zone Guide Support, press the <<1>> key to open the |cFFFFFFGroup & Activity Finder|r and select |cFFFFFFZone Guide|r. You can also access the Zone Guide from the |cFFFFFFAnnouncements|r Panel and the |cFFFFFFMap|r. The Guide provides a description of the zone, lists featured achievements available in the zone, and tracks Map Completion totals. 

Each icon under |cFFFFFFMap Completion|r represents a feature in the zone and your progress toward completing those features. Mousing over each icon describes what the icon represents and includes details on your progress.

A button below the zone panel assists you in finding objectives in the zone. For example, if you have not completed the Main Story Quests of the zone, pressing this button shows you where you need to go to start or continue those quests. If you completed the zone's Main Story Quests, the button guides you to other features in the zone, such as Wayshrines, Delves, and Striking Locales.
Target:
지역 가이드는 여러분들이 플레이하며 지역을 클리어하는 것을 도와줄 것입니다. 지역 가이드에는 지역에 있는 다양한 위치들의 목록과 액티비티들을 찾을 수 있으며, 그런 지역들로 바로 갈 수 있게 도와줍니다.

만약 지역 가이드가 있는 지역에 있다면, <<1>>키를 눌러 |cFFFFFF그룹 & 액티비티 찾기|r를 열고 |cFFFFFF지역 가이드|r를 선택하십시오. |cFFFFFF알림|r 패널이나 |cFFFFFF지도|r에서도 지역 가이드를 찾을 수 있습니다. 가이드는 지역에 대한 설명과, 지역에 있는 다양한 도전과제 목록, 그리고 전체 맵 클리어율을 보여줍니다.

|cFFFFFF완료 상황|r에 있는 각각의 아이콘은 지역에 있는 특징들을 나타내고 이것들을 클리어하기 위한 진척도를 보여줍니다. 각각의 아이콘에 마우스를 올려놓음으로써 해당 아이콘이 무엇을 의미하는지, 그리고 얼마나 진척이 되었는지에 대해 볼 수 있습니다.

지역 패널 아래에 있는 버튼은 지역의 목표를 찾는 데 도움을 줍니다. 예를 들어, 만약 당신이 해당 지역의 메인 스토리 퀘스트를 클리어하지 않았다면, 이 버튼을 누르면 이 퀘스트들을 클리어하기 위해서 어디로 가야 하는지 알려줍니다. 만약 해당 지역의 메인 스토리 퀘스트를 클리어했다면, 이 버튼은 성소, 탐사지, 눈에 띄는 장소들과 같은 다른 곳들로 안내합니다.

Source: Elsweyr is the 2019 chapter.\n\nDragons rage over the province of Elsweyr for the first time in hundreds of years, and the kingdom of Anequina burns in their wake. Behind them marches a rogue Imperial legion and an army of undead, sifting through the wreckage for something that could alter the world and the night sky above forever. Join the Imperial Battlemage Abnur Tharn and the Khajiiti Defense Force in turning back the dark forces assembled against them and restoring Khajiit rule over Northern Elsweyr.
Target: 엘스웨어는 2019년의 챕터입니다.\n\n수백 년 만에 처음으로 드래곤들의 분노가 엘스웨어 지방을 뒤덮고, 아네퀴나 왕국은 불 타오릅니다. 드래곤들의 뒤에는 도적 제국 군단과 언데드 군단이 행진하고, 잔해를 샅샅이 헤치며 세상과 밤하늘을 영원히 바꿀 무언가를 찾고 있습니다. 제국 전투마법사 아브너 탄, 카짓 방위군과 함께 자신들에 대항하여 조직된 어둠의 세력을 되돌리고 북부 엘스웨어에 대한 카짓 민족의 지배력을 회복해야 합니다.

Midyear Mayhem is a seasonal event focused on PvP that takes place in Cyrodiil, Battlegrounds arenas, and the Imperial City's districts. During Midyear Mayhem, you can win honor and bonus rewards by following the steps below:

• Visit the in-game Crown Store to acquire the "Midyear Mayhem" quest. Turn the quest in to Predicant Maera, who you can find at any battleground camp or at your Alliance War faction's main gate in Cyrodiil.
• Complete the quest to receive your Scroll of Pelinal's Ferocity and a Pelinal's Midyear Boon Box.
• Use the scroll to enjoy a two-hour, 100% buff in the Alliance War, Imperial City, and Battlegrounds. This applies to both Alliance Points gained and Experience gains for PvP player kills.

You can keep the Scroll of Pelinal's Ferocity and re-use it for the duration of the event. If you already completed the quest in last year's event, the scroll you received then will work, too. If you previously earned the scroll and misplaced it, don't worry. You can pick up another scroll from Predicant Maera for 100 gold or 100 Alliance Points.

Those who claim victory on the field of battle can earn a special collectible that is available only during the Midyear Mayhem event: the Midyear Victor's Laurel Wreath. To earn this glorious headdress, you must unlock the "Star-Made Knight" achievement by completing each of the seven Midyear Mayhem event Achievements:

• Mayhem Connoisseur
• Echo of Pelinal's Fury
• Hand of the Whitestrake
• Wrath of the Whitestrake
• Pelinavant the Scourge
• Pelinaline the Bloody
• Pelinerrif Insurgent

New Life Festival runs during the second half of Evening Star (December) into the beginning of Morning Star (January). During this time, you can enjoy a 100% Experience buff, obtain a skin that gives you the appearance of a frost atronach, and earn a host of unique New Life Festival themed items.

To participate in the festivities, navigate to the Crown Store's Events section to acquire the "New Life Festival Scroll" free of charge. Once you complete the introductory quests, you gain the opportunity to complete up to nine different daily quests, each themed to Tamriel's different races and located in their respective zones. These include:

•	Castle Charm Challenge (Breton)
•	Fish Boon Feast (Argonian)
•	Lava Foot Stomp (Dark Elf)
•	Mud Ball Merriment (Wood Elf)
•	Signal Fire Sprint (Redguard)
•	Snow Bear Plunge (Nord)
•	Stonetooth Bash (Orc)
•	The Trial of Five-Clawed Guile (Khajiit)
•	War Orphan's Sojourn (High Elf)

In addition, you can drink Breda's Magnificent Mead (located in a keg in the New Life pavilion) to gain a 100% Experience buff for two hours.

During the Undaunted Celebration, enjoy bonus rewards for completing Dungeons of any difficulty.

To start, simply jump into a Dungeon—either through the Dungeon Finder or by traveling directly to the Dungeon via a Wayshrine or your Map.

During the Undaunted Celebration, you can earn Undaunted Reward Boxes by defeating the final boss of any Dungeon. The first time you do this in a day, you also earn an Exceptional box, with even more rewards inside.

Source: If an upgraded Trowel is used to expose a Fissure, it will not deal damage to the Antiquity. Furthermore, if two Fissures can be connected by a path of dirt and rocks that are at exactly the same height, exposing the Fissure will cause an explosive chain reaction! The first step in uncovering an Antiquity is Scrying for it. Gazing into the Antiquarian's Eye will allow you to expand your awareness and mystically search for these hidden treasures.

In order to Scry for an Antiquity, you must be in the same Zone as the Antiquity, and you must have a relevant Lead (if the Antiquity requires it).

To begin Scrying, open your Codex and select the Antiquity you wish to Scry for from the Scryable list. (If the Antiquity does not appear on that list, you cannot Scry for it.) Once you've made your selection, you'll be taken to a view of the Antiquarian's Eye.

When you first begin your journey as an Antiquarian, your Antiquities Codex will appear rather sparse. This is because the majority of Antiquities are hidden!

In order to learn about the existence of these undiscovered Antiquities, you'll need to uncover Leads. Most Antiquities require you to find a Lead before you can Scry for them.

Excavating a hidden Antiquity consumes its Lead, so you'll need to find another Lead to Scry for that Antiquity again. However, your Codex will retain all the details you've learned about that Antiquity so far.

You can find Leads all over Tamriel and beyond. Try speaking with merchants, exploring the world, searching for treasure chests, slaying Bosses, fishing, stealing …. Antiquity Leads can pop up almost anywhere!

One final note: Leads will expire after a long period of time, so be sure to track down hidden Antiquities in a timely fashion!

The Antiquities Codex allows you to see all of the Antiquities you can Scry for, and all of the Antiquities you previously uncovered. Any time you want to search for an Antiquity, the Codex should be your first stop.

The first entry in the Antiquities Codex is the Scryable list. This list displays all of the Antiquities you can currently search for. Select an Antiquity from this list to begin Scrying. Remember that you can only Scry for Antiquities found in the zone you're currently standing in!

The remaining entries in the Codex list Antiquities by zone. This list allows you to see what Antiquities you've found, how many times you've found them, and any Lore Entries you've uncovered for those Antiquities.

Every Antiquity has at least one Lore Entry associated with it. You'll uncover a Lore Entry by successfully excavating that Antiquity. Some Antiquities have more than one Lore Entry; in that case, you'll uncover a new Entry every time you successfully excavate it, until you've found them all.

Once you successfully Scry for an Antiquity, you'll need to venture out into the world in order to find it.

To begin with, open your Zone Map. The map will display a number of "Dig Sites." Only one of these Dig Sites contain the Antiquity. The more Foci you obtain while Scrying, the fewer Dig Sites will appear on the map—down to just one, if you claimed all the Foci.

Once you venture to a Dig Site, your compass will glow, much like a Quest step that requires you to search the area. In much the same way, you'll need to investigate your surroundings to find the Antiquity's resting place.

You can use the Antiquarian's Eye from your Quickslot, or from your Collections menu, to point the way toward the nearest possible location for the Antiquity. However, you can only call on the Antiquarian's Eye in this way every so often, so be sure to look around while you search.

The visible cue you're looking for is a mound of dirt with subtle sparkles floating upwards from it. The dirt may match the terrain's coloration, so keep a sharp eye out. Purchasing the Keen Eye passive may help you spot these dirt mounds more quickly.

Mythic Items are one-piece set items that provide a powerful ability. These abilities are listed on each Mythic Item. Mythic Items can only be worn by characters that are level 50 and have at least 160 Champion Points. You can only equip one Mythic Item at a time and equipping a new Mythic Item requires unequipping any other Mythic Items your character has on.


Mythic Items are acquired through the Antiquities system. Once you've acquired a Mythic Item, it is bound to your account. You can have multiple copies of the same Mythic Item and share Mythic Items with your other characters using the Bank.


You cannot trade or sell Mythic Items to other players. You can sell Mythic Items to Merchants and you can deconstruct Mythic Items to create leads for Antiquities.

Werewolf is a unique skill line you can acquire. The Werewolf Skill Line grants access to a powerful Ultimate ability that transforms you into a savage wolfbeast, complete with a full set of Active Abilities to use while transformed.

To obtain the Werewolf Skill Line, you must become infected by special Werewolf monsters that are only active during certain times of the day and in certain locations. You can also have another player infect you with Lycanthropy, though this must be done at a special Werewolf ritual site.

You can cure Lycanthropy at any time by finding a Priest of Arkay in major cities, but this removes access to the Werewolf Skill Line. You can re-obtain the Skill Line again later and your progress will be preserved.

When Scrying for an Antiquity with the Antiquarian's Eye, you begin at the large crystal in the bottom-middle. This crystal indicates how many turns you have remaining. When the crystal is totally depleted, your Scrying session ends.

Your goal is to claim the glowing Foci scattered across the lens. Every Foci you claim eliminates one possible Dig Site from your map, narrowing and expediting your search. You must acquire at least one Foci to begin searching for the Antiquity.

To move toward the Foci, select a facet adjacent to your area of control. This will add that facet—and all facets of the same type that touch it—to your owned area. In this way, you can claim more and more facets as you Scry.

If you don't acquire all the Foci, you can return to the Codex and Scry for the same Antiquity again. There is no cost associated with trying again, and obtaining more Foci the second time will narrow down the Antiquity's possible locations.

As you advance the Excavation Skill Line, you'll unlock additional tools to aid you in your digging efforts. Both of these tools require you to build up Intuition by using the Hand Brush, and both depend on the elevation of the chunks surrounding where you use them, so be sure to plan your moves carefully.

The Trowel allows you to dig deeply, removing several layers of dirt and rock from a single chunk of the Excavation site. Once upgraded, it can safely trigger Fissures, allowing you to control their detonation, and even chain their explosions together!

The Heavy Shovel can remove a large area of dirt in a single action. It only affects adjacent chunks of the same height as the chunk you select. Use Heavy Shovel to flatten an area quickly, or to remove huge amounts of soil in a hurry. Once upgraded, you have a chance to not consume any Intuition when you use the Heavy Shovel.

Source: The first phase of an Excavation involves locating the Antiquity's location within the dirt, using the Antiquarian's Eye to Augur for it. When you Augur, the chunk of dirt you select will light up. The brighter and greener the light, the closer that chuck is to the Antiquity, with brilliant green indicating the Antiquity's exact location.\n\nOnce you've located the Antiquity, you'll need to uncover it, using your Hand Brush. In lower-difficulty Excavations, the Hand Brush alone can uncover the sought Antiquity. More challenging Excavations, however, require the use of other tools, which you can unlock by leveling up the Antiquarian Skill Line.

Source:
There are 4 types of indicators:
• A faint red outline with no glow: indicates that the Antiquity is at least five chunks of dirt away.
• An orange outline with a subtle glow: indicates that the Antiquity is 3-4 chunks of dirt away.
• A yellow outline with a strong glow: indicates the Antiquity is nearby, 1-2 chunks of dirt away.
• Finally, a bright green outline with a strong, pulsating glow: indicates the Antiquity is directly beneath the Augured chunk.

You can only use your Augur skill a limited number of times during an Excavation. However, using the Augur skill does not consume your limited number of turns for the Excavation, so don't be afraid to use this important skill to give yourself an edge.

Finally, keep in mind: at first, your Augur skill can only detect the Antiquity starting from the lowest, darkest layers of dirt in an Excavation. Once upgraded, it can detect the Antiquity through the middle and lowest layers. This means you may need to remove some dirt before you can successfully Augur for the Antiquity.

Source:
Attempting to excavate more difficult Antiquities often leads to new challenges.

First, you will find that many Antiquities are buried near additional items, known as Bonus Loot. These rewards—while not as valuable as an Antiquity—still provide added benefit to your Excavation.

After you excavate an Antiquity, you can continue to dig for any Bonus Loot still hidden in the dirt. Note, however, that the Augur skill does not reveal Bonus Loot, and you can only keep Bonus Loot if you successfully excavate the Antiquity.

You may also stumble upon Fissures; these small pockets of volatile gas often appear near rarer Antiquities. Removing the last chunk of dirt from a fissure will trigger a detonation, damaging the Antiquity. Upgrading the Trowel can turn these explosions to your benefit by removing large amounts of dirt in a single action. But be wary—these explosions can break an Antiquity and end your excavation in an instant.
Target:
Attempting to excavate more difficult Antiquities often leads to new challenges.

First, you will find that many Antiquities are buried near additional items, known as Bonus Loot. These rewards—while not as valuable as an Antiquity—still provide added benefit to your Excavation.

After you excavate an Antiquity, you can continue to dig for any Bonus Loot still hidden in the dirt. Note, however, that the Augur skill does not reveal Bonus Loot, and you can only keep Bonus Loot if you successfully excavate the Antiquity.

You may also stumble upon Fissures; these small pockets of volatile gas often appear near rarer Antiquities. Removing the last chunk of dirt from a fissure will trigger a detonation, damaging the Antiquity. Upgrading the Trowel can turn these explosions to your benefit by removing large amounts of dirt in a single action. But be wary—these explosions can break an Antiquity and end your excavation in an instant.

Source:
The last step in acquiring an Antiquity is Excavation. During an Excavation, you work to remove the Antiquity from the dirt, without breaking it, and within the time allotted.

To begin an Excavation, you must first Scry for the Antiquity, and then locate its exact burial spot within its Dig Site. Once you interact with the Antiquity's dirt mound, the Excavation begins.

You have a limited number of actions you can take during an Excavation, indicated by the Intuition meter at the top of the screen, and by the daylight remaining. When you've used up your limited actions, the dig is over.

If you fail to Excavate an Antiquity (whether by breaking it, or by running out of turns), the Dig Site will disappear. Don't worry, though. You can find it again, somewhere within the same Dig Site on your map.
Target:

You have a limited number of actions you can take during an Excavation, indicated by the Intuition meter at the top of the screen, and by the daylight remaining. When you've used up your limited actions, the dig is over.

If you fail to Excavate an Antiquity (whether by breaking it, or by running out of turns), the Dig Site will disappear. Don't worry, though. You can find it again, somewhere within the same Dig Site on your map.

Source: Race Change Tokens allow you to change everything that Appearance Change Tokens do, in addition to race. Changing your race will refund any skill points you have invested in your racial skill line, and will carry your progress over to the new race's skill line. Changing your race does not grant or remove racial crafting motif knowledge.\n\nPlease note that certain collectibles are race and/or gender limited—if you change to a restricted race or gender with one of these active, it will be deactivated.
Target: 종족 변경 토큰은 종족 외에 외모 변경 토큰이 하는 모든 것도 바꿀 수 있게 해줍니다. 당신의 종족을 바꾸는 것은 당신이 당신의 종족 스킬 라인에 투자한 모든 스킬 포인트를 환불되며, 당신의 새로운 종족의 스킬 라인으로 넘어갈 것 입니다. 종족을 바꾼다고 해서 종족 제작 모티브 지식을 부여하거나 제거하지 않습니다\n\n특정 수집품은 종족 및 / 또는 성별이 제한되어 있음을 유념하십시오. 이러한 수집품은 제한된 인종 또는 성별로 변경하면 비활성화됩니다.

Source:
Killing a target with the Blade of Woe has a chance to grant you Dried Blood or Tainted Blood, which can be used to craft gear in the Assassins League style.

The Blade of Woe can only be used on humanoids, cannot be used in Group Dungeons or in Trials, and cannot be used against certain powerful enemies.

Using the Blade of Woe does not prevent you from being witnessed by bystanders, so keep an eye on your surroundings!

비통의 단검은 인간에만 사용할 수 있고, 그룹 던전 또는 트라이얼에서 사용할 수 없으며, 단검이 통하지 않는 특정 강력한 적도 있습니다..

비통의 단검을 사용한다고 해서 구경꾼들이 목격하는 것을 막을 수는 없으니, 주위를 잘 살피세요!

Source: As one of the king's invited champions, partake in every challenge and pleasure Orsinium has to offer. A Call to Arms grants access to Chef Chukka-Jekka on the upper level of the Sanctum.

Restoring the Order unlocks the door to the Dragonguard Sanctum on the lower level, which leads to the Ancient Dragonguard Item Set stations in the Dragonguard Armory.

Reforging the Dragonguard grants access to Achievement Furnisher, Martina Ocella, who has a number of Southern Elsweyr-themed furnishings for sale on the upper level. This also unlocks a new quest, "The Good Bits," from Dahfnar on the upper level. Completing this quest teaches you how to harvest the Dragon's Rheum alchemy reagent from slain dragons.

Source: Dragons rarely stay in one place for long. Once a Dragon chooses a target, it soars to that location and begins its onslaught. Source:
During Witches Festival, you will earn special rewards by defeating boss monsters anywhere in the world. These boss monsters will drop a special box called a "Plunder Skull." The first of each boss type defeated per day per account will instead drop an exceptional type of Plunder Skull called a "Dremora Plunder Skull." The first of any boss you defeat a day will also drop Event Tickets.

Plunder Skulls
These can contain a bevy of items including:
• Hollowjack Motif Books and Chapters
• Witches Festival Provisioning Recipes
• Witches Festival Furnishing Recipes
• Witches Festival Furnishings
• Witches Festival Themed Masks
• Apple Bobbing & Skeletal Marionette Memento Runebox Fragments
• Various Crafting Materials
• Various Creepy Crawlies

Dremora Plunder Skulls
These can include the items from a normal Plunder Skull, and will also contain one of two Dremora Motif Chapters based on the type of boss killed:
• Arena Final Bosses: Bows or Legs
• Insurgent Bosses: Daggers or Gloves
• Delve Bosses: Staves or Belts
• Dungeon Final Bosses: Helmets or Maces
• Public Dungeon, Sweeper, and Quest Bosses: Shields or Boots
• Trial Final Bosses: Swords or Chests
• World Bosses: Shoulders or Axes
Dremora Plunder Skulls may also contain additional rewards, such as Witches Festival Writs and Glenmoril Treasure Maps.

Event Tickets
During Witches Festival, you can earn two Event Tickets per day per account by defeating any boss monster. These can be traded for special items at The Impresario, Event Merchant.

Source: Attributes have been re-balanced in this update. To compensate you, all your attribute points have been refunded. Please read the patch notes for a complete list of changes.

Source:
Enchanted berries are available for a limited time only through The Impresario, so make sure you get them while you can.

Evolving an indrik requires you to have a Nascent Indrik and all 4 Enchanted Berries of the same type. After all 4 berries have been acquired, combine them in the Collections menu to evolve the Nascent Indrik into the associated evolution. So, if you have a Nascent Indrik and the 4 different Dawnwood Enchanted Berries, the Nascent Indrik becomes a Dawnwood Indrik.

Once a Nascent Indrik evolves into a different form, the Nascent Indrik mount collectible is locked and a new Indrik mount collectible is unlocked. If you want another Nascent Indrik to use or to evolve into a different Indrik form you have not unlocked, you will need to acquire another Nascent Indrik to unlock the mount collectible again.

Source:
As you earn glory in PvP, you can receive Pelinal's Midyear Boon Boxes in addition to your regular Rewards for the Worthy containers. This year, you can also earn the Boon Boxes from the repeatable Town, Battle, Bounty, Conquest, Scouting, Warfront, and Imperial City District quests in Cyrodiil as well as the Battlegrounds repeatable quests. These unique event boxes contain Tel Var Stones and a chance to receive one of these items:

• Transmute Crystals
• Alchemy reagents
• PvP consumables such as repair kits, forward camps, and siege weapons
• Motif pages for the Alliance and Akaviri styles
• Style items for your Alliance
• Akaviri style items
• Coldharbour siege weapons
• Prismatic Runestones
• Books of Pelinal housing items
• Alliance Standard-Bearer Emblems (used to obtain Alliance Standard-Bearer Emotes)

In addition, Style Pages for the new Second Legion Outfit Style occasionally drop from bosses in Imperial City and the Imperial City Sewers. You can also find Legion Zero Outfit Style pages on these bosses, but at a reduced rate.

During the event, all nodes in Cyrodiil and the Imperial City drop double their regular resources, and the Cyrodiil PvP merchant Adhazabi Aba-daro (known as "The Golden") stocks Alliance War Legendary-quality jewelry. During the first weekend of the event, you can purchase necklaces, and during the second weekend, you can acquire rings. You can find Adhazabi in the Western Elsweyr Gate, Northern High Rock Gate, or Southern Morrowind Gate once you enter Cyrodiil.

Event Tickets

During Midyear Mayhem, you can earn two Event Tickets per day from any Cyrodiil or Battlegrounds daily quest, and two Event Tickets per day for completing an Imperial City district daily quest. These can be traded for special items at the Event Merchant (The Impresario), including Indrik Summoning Feathers and Evolution Berries.

This year, you can also earn the Boon Boxes from the repeatable Town, Battle, Bounty, Conquest, Scouting, Warfront, and Imperial City District quests in Cyrodiil as well as the Battlegrounds repeatable quests. These unique event boxes contain Tel Var Stones and a chance to receive one of these items:

• Transmute Crystals
• Alchemy reagents
• PvP consumables such as repair kits, forward camps, and siege weapons
• Motif pages for the Alliance and Akaviri styles
• Style items for your Alliance
• Akaviri style items
• Coldharbour siege weapons
• Prismatic Runestones
• Books of Pelinal housing items
• Alliance Standard-Bearer Emblems (used to obtain Alliance Standard-Bearer Emotes)

In addition, Style Pages for the new Second Legion Outfit Style occasionally drop from bosses in Imperial City and the Imperial City Sewers. You can also find Legion Zero Outfit Style pages on these bosses, but at a reduced rate.

During the event, all nodes in Cyrodiil and the Imperial City drop double their regular resources, and the Cyrodiil PvP merchant Adhazabi Aba-daro (known as \"The Golden"") stocks Alliance War Legendary-quality jewelry. During the first weekend of the event
column4: you can purchase necklaces
column5: and during the second weekend
column6: you can acquire rings. You can find Adhazabi in the Western Elsweyr Gate
column8:
or Southern Morrowind Gate once you enter Cyrodiil.

Event Tickets

During Midyear Mayhem
column9: you can earn two Event Tickets per day from any Cyrodiil or Battlegrounds daily quest
column10: and two Event Tickets per day for completing an Imperial City district daily quest. These can be traded for special items at the Event Merchant (The Impresario)
column11: including Indrik Summoning Feathers and Evolution Berries."

Every New Life Festival quest gives a single New Life Gift Box, which can contain a variety of unique rewards including:

•	Crafting Ingredients
•	New Life Toys
•	Skinchanger Motif Chapters
•	New Life Runeboxes
•	Provisioning Recipes
•	Light Source Furnishings
•	Wolfsbane Incense
•	New Life Charity Writs
•	Deep Winter Writs

New Life Charity Writs, found only as a rare drop inside New Life Gift Boxes, require you to craft simple furnishings for citizens of Tamriel that are in need. Completed writs can be turned in at any writ drop-off area throughout the world. You earn the new Crystalfrost skin for completing twelve New Life Charity Writs.

Deep Winter Writs are similar to the New Life Charity Writs in acquisition and requirements. Completing any Deep Winter Writ will award a Skaal Outfit Style Page.

Event Tickets

Outfit Customization
Each time you customize an Outfit there is a cost associated, no matter how small the change. When customizing, you can swap your weapons to better coordinate your look.

Outfits and Weapons
Weapon styles are grouped according to the Skill Line associated with them. Any weapon from a Skill Line can take on the associated style, whether it is equipped or not.

Unlocking Outfit Styles
Each Outfit Style will display a hint revealing how it can be unlocked.

Source: The Chat Window is your tool to communicate with other players in The Elder Scrolls Online universe. By default this window is located on the lower left hand side of the In-Game View. Source: To interact with other players in the world, aim your targeting reticule at them and hold down the <<1>> key.  This will bring up a radial menu of interact options.  Move your mouse to the option you wish to use and release the <<1>> key to commit to your selection.

Source: There are many objects and people in the world of Tamriel  that you can interact with.  While in the In-Game View mode, when you approach such an object or person and aim your targeting reticule at it, an interact prompt will appear.  Simply press <<1>> to interact with it.

column4: 선택된 아이템을 향상시키기 위해 필요한 재료를 옆에 보여줍니다. 아래의 플러스 버튼을 클릭하여 재료의 양을 추가하면 향상의 성공 확률이 높아집니다. 모든 준비가 되었을 때 <<1>> 키를 눌러 아이템을 향상시키십시오."

Source:
Choose a material to craft using the left and right arrow buttons, and the plus and minus buttons below the material to choose the level of the item, or items, you wish to craft. 

Select a racial style for the items using the left and right arrow buttons. Initially, you will only be able to craft in the racial style of your character, but other racial styles can be unlocked. 

Select a trait to add one of a variety of available enhancements to your items. Researching will unlock new traits.
Target:
왼쪽과 오른쪽 화살표 버튼을 사용하여 제작 재료를 선택하고 재료 아래의 플러스와 마이너스 버튼을 사용하여 제작할 아이템의 레벨을 선택하십시오.

왼쪽과 오른쪽 화살표 버튼를 사용하여 아이템의 종족 스타일을 선택하십시오. 처음에는 본인의 캐릭터의 종족 스타일로만 제작할 수 있지만 다른 종족 스타일들을 해금할 수 있습니다.

제작 시 아이템을 향상시킬 수 있는 특성을 한 가지 선택할 수 있습니다. 연구를 통해 새로운 특성을 해금할 수 있습니다.

Source: If you have an item in your inventory that can be researched an indicator will appear under the selected trait line and the text next to the researchable trait will display "Researchable". Double-click on the item you wish to research and press <<1>> to confirm the research.\n\nThe research process takes time. This time will increase when multiple traits have been researched for a specific trait research line.
Target: 연구 가능한 아이템이 인벤토리에 있을 경우 선택한 특성 라인에 표시되며 특성 옆에 \\"연구가능\"\" 이라고 표시됩니다. 연구하려는 아이템을 두 번 클릭하고 <<1>> 버튼을 눌러 확인하면 연구가 시작됩니다.\n\n연구에는 시간이 걸립니다. 여러 특성 연구가 이미 진행된 연구 라인에서 연구를 진행할수록 이 시간은 더 길어집니다."

Source: Skilled Woodworkers are always seeking to learn new techniques to better their skills at the mill. Finding special crafting books is the key to learning new racial styles, while researching traits allows for the creation of higher quality staves and shields.
Target: 숙련된 목세공사는 항상 제분소에서 실력을 향상시키기 위한 새로운 기술을 배우기 위해 노력합니다. 특별제작서를 찾는 것은 새로운 종족의 스타일을 배우기 위한 성공의 열쇠입니다. 또한 특성을 연구하는 것을 통해 더 높은 품질의 방패와 지팡이를 제작할 수 있습니다.

Source:
When a Provisioner finds a new recipe they can learn it by using it from their inventory. This action will add it to their recipe book.

Provisioners create known food and drinks by utilizing one of the many usable cooking fires found throughout the world.

Foods give long term boosts to Health, Magicka or Stamina while Drinks improve their recovery rates.
Target:
요리사가 새로운 레시피를 찾았을 경우 인벤토리 창 내에 있는 레시피를 사용해서 새 요리법을 배울 수 있습니다. 배운 요리는 요리책에 추가됩니다.

요리사는 세계 각지에 있는 요리용 화로를 사용해 알고있는 음식과 음료를 만들 수 있습니다.

음식을 먹었을 경우 최대 체력이나 매지카 혹은 스태미나가 증가하며, 음료를 마셨을 경우 체력이나 매지카 혹은 스태미나의 재생 능력이 증가하는 장시간 효과를 제공합니다.

As a member of this force, slay Molag Bal's minions in the Imperial City's six districts, or plumb the depths of the Imperial Sewers in search of treasure.

Be warned: enemy bannermen are everywhere, and they will sell their lives dearly.

During your adventures in the Imperial City, you will encounter a valuable new currency known as Tel Var Stones. Claim as many stones as you can to purchase powerful new items. Crush the Daedra, grow in power, and lead your Alliance to victory in the Imperial City.
Target:
이 세력의 일원으로서 임페리얼 시티 6개 구역의 몰락 발 하수인들을 처치하거나, 보물을 찾아 제국 하수구의 깊숙한 곳을 파헤치세요.

주의하세요. 적의 기수들은 어디에나 있고, 그들은 그들의 목숨을 기꺼이 버릴 것입니다.

임페리얼 시티에서 모험을 하는 동안, 당신은 텔 바 스톤이라고 알려진 값진 새로운 화폐를 만나게 될 것입니다. 가능한 한 많은 스톤을 요구하여 강력한 아이템을 구입하십시오. 데이드라를 격파하고, 세력을 키우고, 임페리얼 시티에서 동맹을 승리로 이끄세요.

Spending Points:
Once inside the preferred Minor Constellation, points can be spent in the skills that have a "-" and "+" below them.

Each point spent in a Minor Constellation increases its rank. Once the Minor Constellation reaches a specific rank, passive abilities unlock for your character. If you respec your character, all passive abilities gained via rank in a specific Minor Constellation are lost until the appropriate number of points are reinvested.

Source:
Dye Tools
•	The Paint Brush allows you to apply a dye to an individual dye slot on a single armor piece
•	The Paint Bucket allows you to apply a dye to the same slot across all equipped armor pieces
•	The Eraser Tool allows you to remove an applied dye from a dye slot
•	The Eye Dropper allows you to copy existing colors you've already applied to other dye slots
•	The Set Fill Tool allows you to apply colors to saved sets of your dye slots

Note: Dyeing a piece of armor binds it to your account.

Source:
You may hire a Guild Trader at a Guild Trader station if no other guild has purchased their services. If another guild owns the services of a Guild Trader you may place a blind bid to try to acquire them when they become available.

Bidding occurs throughout the week, but players may only bid on one Trader per cycle. If you acquire the services of a Trader through bidding, their services will be yours for one week's time. 

Remember: You must continue bidding on a Trader to retain their services.

Source: Skillful fishermen will learn to use the optimal bait for the type of fish they are trying to catch.
Target: 숙련된 낚시꾼은 원하는 물고기를 잡기에 적합한 미끼를 사용하는 법을 알게 될 것입니다.

Source: It is not necessary to purchase or equip a fishing pole. Every character already has one. Your fishing pole automatically becomes active when you attempt to fish. You will, however, be required to collect or purchase bait. \n\nWhen you have bait in your inventory, you can see it by using the Consumables filter. If you have access to the Craft Bag, you can find your bait under the Provisioning filter. Bugs, worms, and guts are common bait. Try sharing a fishing hole with other adventures to increase your chances of rare fish!
Target: 낚시대를 구매하거나 장비해야 할 필요가 없습니다. 모든 캐릭터는 이미 낚시대를 소지하고 있습니다. 낚시를 할 때 낚시대가 자동으로 활성화 될 것입니다. 하지만 플레이어는 미끼를 획득하거나 구매해야 합니다. \n\n소지품 내에 미끼가 있을 경우 소비아이템(Consumables filter)창에서 미끼를 확인할 수 있습니다. 제작가방(Craft Bag)이 있을 경우 요리(Provisioning filter)창에서 미끼를 찾을 수 있습니다. 흔하게 사용되는 미끼는 벌레, 지렁이, 동물의 내장입니다. 다양한 모험과 함께 낚시를 통해 희귀한 생선을 얻어보세요!

Source: Visiting a Stable Master will allow your character to take Riding Lessons. Riding Lessons will allow your character to increase their Speed, Stamina, and Carry Capacity attributes in the area of mount riding.

Source: Although there are many stables throughout Tamriel, not all have Stable Masters. Search stables in major cities to locate a Stable Master.
Target: 탐리엘(Tamriel)에 있는 모든 마구간에 마구간 주인(Stable Master)이 있는 건 아닙니다. 마구간 주인(Stable Master)을 찾으신다면 대도시의 마구간을 둘러보세요.

Source: Enchanters create glyphs by combining runes of three different types: Potency, Aspect and Essence. Potency will determine the required level and strength of the resulting glyph, Aspect will determine its quality, and Essence will determine its magical effect. A skilled Enchanter will collect and combine any runes he finds in an effort to decipher their hidden language and unlock their magical properties.
Target: 마법부여가는 포텐시(Potency), 애스펙트(Aspect), 에센스(Essence)의 총 세 가지의 룬을 결합하여 글리프를 제작할 수 있습니다. 포텐시(Potency)는 요구 레벨과 글리프의 영향력을 결정하며, 애스펙트(Aspect)는 품질을, 에센스(Essence)는 마법 효과를 결정합니다. 숙련된 마법부여가는 룬에 숨겨진 마법 효과를 개방하고 언어를 해독하기 위해 룬들을 수집하고 결합합니다.

Source: All reagents have hidden traits which determine a product's effects. Similar traits from different reagents must be stacked to bring out their magical qualities. Each trait can be countered by another trait, and if the wrong reagents are mixed together they might cancel each other out. A skilled Alchemist experiments to find reagent combinations that offer the best results.\n\nPoisons that are crafted with positive effects, such as Restore Health, will drain that effect from the target to enhance the poisoner.
Target: 시약 내에는 숨겨진 특성이 있으며 이 특성이 물약의 효과를 결정합니다. 비슷한 특성이 있는 시약을 함께 사용해 제조했을 때 마법적인 특성을 발휘합니다. 각 특성은 다른 특성을 무효화 할 수 있으며, 잘못된 시약을 혼합하면 모든 시약이 무효화 될 수 있습니다. 숙련된 연금술사는 최고의 결과물을 만들 수 있는 시약의 조합법을 찾기 위한 실험을 반복합니다.\n\n체력 재생 효과와 같이 이로운 효과가 있는 시약을 사용해 독약을 만들 경우 독약 성분으로 작용하여 타겟의 능력치를 흡수합니다.

Source: Skilled Clothiers are always seeking to learn new techniques to better their skills at the tannin table. Finding special crafting books is the key to learning new racial styles, and researching traits allows for the creation of higher quality clothing and armor.
Target: 숙련된 재봉사는 항상 타닌 작업대에서 실력을 향상시키기 위한 새로운 기술을 배우기 위해 노력합니다. 특별제작서를 찾는 것은 새로운 종족의 스타일을 배우기 위한 성공의 열쇠입니다. 또한 특성을 연구하는 것을 통해 더 높은 품질의 갑옷과 천옷 제작이 가능해집니다.

Source: A skilled Blacksmith will always seek to learn new techniques to better their skills at the forge. Finding special crafting books is the key to learning new racial styles, and researching traits allows for the creation of higher quality weapons and armor.

Source: The racial skills of the Bretons reflect their affinity for the arcane, increasing their base magicka, magicka recovery, light armor, alliance point gain, spell resistance, and cost reduction of spells, allowing them to cast spells with little pause.
Target: 브레튼의 종족 스킬은 아케인과의 친화력을 반영합니다. 최대 매지카량, 매지카 재생, 천옷 숙련도, 연합 점수 획득, 마법 저항력, 스펠 코스트 감소에 보너스를 얻습니다. 이러한 보너스는 계속해서 주문을 시전할 수 있도록 해줍니다.

Source: The racial skills of the Orcs reflect their native harsh mountain environment, giving them bonuses to heavy armor use, sprinting, weapon damage, inspiration gain, weapon proficiency, as well as base health and stamina.
Target: 오크의 종족 스킬은 그들의 고향인 험준한 산악지형을 반영합니다. 중갑 숙련도, 달리기, 무기 데미지, 제작 숙련도 획득량, 무기 숙련도, 최대 체력량, 최대 스테미나량에서 보너스를 얻습니다.

Source: The racial skills of the Redguards reflect their ancestral legacy as sword masters, giving them bonuses to shields, base stamina, stamina recovery, movement, and duration of effects from food. Their ability to flow in martial combat is unparalleled.
Target: 레드가드의 종족 스킬은 소드 마스터였던 조상의 유산을 반영합니다. 방패 숙련도, 최대 스테미나량, 스테미나 회복량, 움직임, 음식 지속시간에서 보너스를 얻습니다. 이들의 전투 능력은 그 누구와도 비교할 수 없습니다.

Source: The racial skills of the Nords reflect their strong and hardy natures, giving them bonuses to two-handed weapon use, duration of effects from drinks, physical, spell, and frost resistance, ultimate generation, as well as base health and stamina.
Target: 노드의 종족 스킬은 그들의 힘과 강인한 천성을 반영합니다. 양손 무기 숙련도, 음료 지속시간, 궁극기 생성, 물리,주문,냉기 저항력, 최대 체력량, 최대 스테미나량 에서 보너스를 얻습니다.

Source: The racial skills of the Dark Elves reflect their intellect and agility, giving them bonuses in dual wielding, flame and lava resistance, weapon and spell damage, and base magicka and stamina. These bonuses allow them to adapt to anything.
Target: 다크 엘프의 종족 스킬은 그들의 지성과 민첩성을 반영합니다. 쌍수 무기 숙련도, 불과 용암 저항력, 무기와 주문 데미지, 최대 매지카량, 최대 스테미나량에서 보너스를 얻습니다. 이러한 보너스는 그들이 어떤 상황에서든 적응할 수 있도록 해줄 것입니다.

Source: The racial skills of the High Elves reflect their magical affinity by increasing their spell damage, resource recovery, base magicka, and experience gain. These innate bonuses help define the race as proud and powerful spell casters.
Target: 하이 엘프의 종족 스킬들은 그들의 마법 친화력을 반영합니다. 스펠 데미지, 매지카 재생력, 최대 매지카량, 경험치 획득량에서 보너스를 얻습니다. 이러한 보너스는 하이엘프를 자부심 있고 강력한 주문 캐스터로 만들어줍니다.

Source: The racial skills of the Argonians reflect their people's perilous swamp environment; giving them bonuses to healing done, restoration staves, disease resistance, resources gained from consuming potions, swimming speed, as well as base health and magicka.
Target: 아르고니안의 종족 스킬은 그들의 위험한 늪 환경을 반영합니다. 치유량, 치유 지팡이 숙련도,질병 저항력, 수영속도, 포션을 통한 자원 회복, 최대 체력량, 최대 매지카량에서 보너스를 얻습니다.

Source: The racial skills of the feline Khajiit reflect their natural versatility and guile, giving them bonuses to pickpocketing, stealth, resource recovery, as well as base health, magicka, and stamina.  These bonuses help them thrive in many ventures of life.
Target: 고양이과인 카짓의 종족 스킬은 타고난 다재다능함과 교활함을 반영합니다. 자물쇠따기, 은신, 그리고  체력,스테미나, 매지카 회복력에서 보너스를 얻습니다. 이러한 보너스는 삶에서 마주할 여러 위험들을 잘 헤쳐나가도록 도와줄 것입니다.

Source: The diversified racial skills of the Wood Elves reflect their woodland affinity. Improved archery, base stamina, stamina recovery, stealth detection, movement speed, reduced fall damage, and poison resistance make them dangerous foes and gifted hunters.
Target: The diversified racial skills of the Wood Elves reflect their woodland affinity. Improved archery, base stamina, stamina recovery, stealth detection, movement speed, reduced fall damage, and poison resistance make them dangerous foes and gifted hunters.

Target: 신생 메이지 길드에게 본부가 필요해졌을 때, 그들은 임페리얼 시티에서 가까운 오래된 에일리드 구역을 점유하고 그 내부를 아케인 대학으로 재건했습니다. 지금은 벌레 교단이 점거했지만, 그 전에도 이미 몰라그 발의 차원융합 도중에 심하게 손상되었던 상태였습니다.

Source: The crumbling Dwarven fortifications of Ald Carac are said to date to the time of the War of the First Council, early in the First Era.
Target: 알드 카락 지역의 드워프 요새의 붕괴는 제 1 시대 초반에 있었던 전쟁에 대한 첫 회의 때 까지 전해졌습니다.

Source: This quarry on the southern slopes of Red Mountain is the source of the granite being used to construct Vivec City—or it was, until the volcano awoke and began once more pouring lava down its foyadas.

Source: Battlegrounds are three team player-vs-player arenas that allow you to test your skills against other players in a number of different game modes. Queuing for a Battleground with a party of fewer than 4 players will fill a group with other players so you will be able to participate. After the Battleground has ended, any players added to your party for the match will be removed and you will be returned to where you were before you entered the Battleground.\n\nTo participate in a Battleground, open the |cFFFFFFActivity Finder|r and select |cFFFFFFBattlegrounds|r. Select if you want to play a |cFFFFFFRandom Battleground|r or a |cFFFFFFSpecific Battleground|r. Press the |cFFFFFFJoin Queue|r button and you will be queued for a Battleground. When the Battleground is ready, you will receive a ready check notification while you are out of combat. Accepting this will confirm you are ready to start the Battleground.
Target: 배틀그라운드는 세 팀으로 이루어진 플레이어 vs 플레이어 경기로써 다양한 게임 모드를 통해 다른 플레이어 상대로 자신의 능력을 시험해볼 수 있습니다. 4인 미만으로 구성된 파티로 배틀그라운드의 대기열을 돌리면, 다른 플레이어를 파티에 참가시켜 게임에 참여할 수 있게 합니다. 배틀그라운드가 끝나면, 각각의 플레이어들은 각자의 파티에서 떠나 배틀그라운드가 시작하기 전에 있던 곳으로 되돌아갑니다.\n\n배틀그라운드에 참여하기 위해선, |cFFFFFF액티비티 찾기|r를 열고 |cFFFFFF배틀그라운드|r를 선택하십시오. |cFFFFFF무작위 배틀그라운드|r 또는 |cFFFFFF특정 배틀그라운드|r중 플레이하고 싶은 것을 선택하십시오. |cFFFFFF대기열 입장|r버튼을 눌러 배틀그라운드의 대기열에 들어갈 수 있습니다. 배틀그라운드가 준비되면, 전투중이 아닐 때 준비 확인 알림을 받게 됩니다. 이 알림을 수락하여 자신이 배틀그라운드를 시작할 준비가 되었음을 알리세요.

Source: The Dark Heart of Skyrim beats from the depths in The Elder Scrolls Online: Greymoor, the latest adventure yet in the Elder Scrolls saga. Source: The Dungeon Finder makes it easy to find a group to play Dungeons with. Through the Dungeon Finder, you can choose to play a random or specific Dungeon. Once a tank, a healer, and two damage dealers are found using the Dungeon Finder, a group will automatically be formed and each player will be teleported to the Dungeon. After completing the Dungeon, you can leave the Dungeon and will be removed from the group and returned to where you were before you entered the Dungeon.\n\nTo use the Dungeon Finder, navigate to the |cFFFFFFActivity Finder|r from the Main Menu <<1>>, then select the |cFFFFFFDungeon Finder|r. Select if you want a random or specific dungeon. Press the |cFFFFFFJoin Queue|r button to be queued for a Dungeon. When the Dungeon is ready, you will receive a ready check notification while you are out of combat. Accepting this confirms that you're ready to start the Dungeon.

던전 파티 찾기는 던전을 플레이할 그룹을 찾기 쉽게 도와줍니다. 던전 파티 찾기를 통해, 무작위 던전 또는 특정 던전을 선택하여 플레이할 수 있습니다. 방어 전담 한 명, 치유 전담 한 명, 공격 전담 두 명이 던전 파티 찾기로 찾아지면, 자동으로 해당 플레이어들끼리 그룹이 맺어지고 던전으로 순간이동 합니다. 던전을 클리어하고 나면, 던전에서 나와 그룹을 떠나고 던전에 들어가기 전에 있었던 곳으로 다시 되돌아갈 수 있습니다.

던전 파티 찾기를 하려면, 메인 메뉴 <<1>>에서 |cFFFFFF액티비티 찾기|r에 들어간 뒤, |cFFFFFF던전 파티 찾기|r를 클릭하십시오.
|cFFFFFF역할|r을 제대로 선택했는지 확인하십시오:
|t48:48:EsoUI/Art//Tutorial/LFG_tank_up.dds|t|cFFFFFF방어 전담|r, |t48:48:EsoUI/Art//Tutorial/LFG_healer_up.dds|t|cFFFFFF치유 전담|r, or |t48:48:EsoUI/Art//Tutorial/LFG_dps_up.dds|t|cFFFFFF공격 전담|r 중 하나입니다. 무작위 던전을 플레이할 것인지, 특정 던전을 클리어할 것인지 오른쪽 위의 드롭 다운 메뉴를 사용하여 선택하십시오. |cFFFFFF대기열 입장|r버튼을 눌러 던전 대기열에 딥장하십시오. 던전이 준비되면, 플레이어가 전투 중이 아닐 때 준비를 확인하는 알림을 받을 것입니다. 이 알림을 수락하면 던전을 시작할 준비가 된 것입니다.

The Zone Guide helps you play through and complete zones. It includes lists of locations and activities found in a zone and helps direct you to these areas.

If you are in a zone that has Zone Guide Support, press <<1>>, select|t48:48:EsoUI/Art/TreeIcons/gamepad/gp_icon_activityFinder.dds|t |cFFFFFFActivity Finder|r, and select |t48:48:EsoUI/Art/TreeIcons/gamepad/gp_tutorial_idexIcon_adventuring.dds|t |cFFFFFFZone Guide|r. You can also access the Zone Guide from the |cFFFFFFAnnouncements|r Panel and the |cFFFFFFMap|r. The Guide provides a description of the zone, lists featured achievements available in the zone, and tracks Map Completion totals. 

Each icon under |cFFFFFFMap Completion|r represents a feature in the zone and your progress toward completing those features. Mousing over each icon describes what the icon represents and includes details on your progress.

A button below the zone panel assists you in finding objectives in the zone. For example, if you have not completed the Main Story Quests of the zone, pressing this button shows you where you need to go to start or continue those quests. If you completed the zone's Main Story Quests, the button guides you to other features in the zone, such as Wayshrines, Delves, and Striking Locales.
Target:
지역 가이드는 여러분들이 플레이하며 지역을 클리어하는 것을 도와줄 것입니다. 지역 가이드에는 지역에 있는 다양한 위치들의 목록과 액티비티들을 찾을 수 있으며, 그런 지역들로 바로 갈 수 있게 도와줍니다.

만약 지역 가이드가 있는 지역에 있다면, <<1>>키를 눌러 |t48:48:EsoUI/Art/TreeIcons/gamepad/gp_icon_activityFinder.dds|t |cFFFFFF그룹 & 액티비티 찾기|r를 열고 |t48:48:EsoUI/Art/TreeIcons/gamepad/gp_tutorial_idexIcon_adventuring.dds|t 
|cFFFFFF지역 가이드|r를 선택하십시오. |cFFFFFF알림|r 패널이나 |cFFFFFF지도|r에서도 지역 가이드를 찾을 수 있습니다. 가이드는 지역에 대한 설명과, 지역에 있는 다양한 도전과제 목록, 그리고 전체 맵 클리어율을 보여줍니다.

|cFFFFFF완료 상황|r에 있는 각각의 아이콘은 지역에 있는 특징들을 나타내고 이것들을 클리어하기 위한 진척도를 보여줍니다. 각각의 아이콘에 마우스를 올려놓음으로써 해당 아이콘이 무엇을 의미하는지, 그리고 얼마나 진척이 되었는지에 대해 볼 수 있습니다.

지역 패널 아래에 있는 버튼은 지역의 목표를 찾는 데 도움을 줍니다. 예를 들어, 만약 당신이 해당 지역의 메인 스토리 퀘스트를 클리어하지 않았다면, 이 버튼을 누르면 이 퀘스트들을 클리어하기 위해서 어디로 가야 하는지 알려줍니다. 만약 해당 지역의 메인 스토리 퀘스트를 클리어했다면, 이 버튼은 성소, 델브, 눈에 띄는 장소들과 같은 다른 곳들로 안내합니다.

|t48:48:EsoUI/Art/LFG/ZoneStories/completionTypeIcon_priorityQuest.dds|t |cFFFFFF지역 스토리 퀘스트|r 는 지역의 메인 스토리 퀘스트입니다.
|t48:48:EsoUI/Art/LFG/ZoneStories/completionTypeIcon_wayshrine.dds|t |cFFFFFF성소|r 는 이미 발견한 성소들에 순간이동을 시켜 줍니다. 성소 근처로 가서 진척도를 올리고 성소의 접근 권한을 얻으십시오.

|t48:48:EsoUI/Art/LFG/ZoneStories/completionTypeIcon_groupDelve.dds|t |cFFFFFF그룹 탐사지|r 은 다수의 플레이어들이 함께 클리어하도록 설계된 던전입니다. 보스를 처치하여 던전을 클리어하십시오.
|t48:48:EsoUI/Art/LFG/ZoneStories/completionTypeIcon_pointOfInterest.dds|t |cFFFFFF흥미로운 장소|r 는 해당 지역의 이야기, 캐릭터, 그리고 장소들을 탐험할 수 있는 독단적인 이야기들입니다. 해당 지역의 퀘스트를 클리어하거나 해당 지역을 발견하여 진척도를 올릴 수 있습니다.
|t48:48:EsoUI/Art/LFG/ZoneStories/completionTypeIcon_strikingLocales.dds|t |cFFFFFF눈에 띄는 장소|r 는 세계에 있는 독특한 전망과 장소들입니다. 이 지역들을 발견하여 진척도를 올리십시오.

The Guild Finder allows players to search for guilds that meet their preferred criteria, and apply to any of the results. If their application is accepted, the interested player is added to the guild. 

Active guilds interested in finding new members populate the Guild Finder. Guildmasters set up a guild listing, including details such as Primary and Secondary Focus, Additional Activities, Roles being sought, Champion Point Minimums, Play Styles, Languages, Core Hours, and more. 

Unguilded players interested in joining a guild can access the Guild Finder by opening the Main Menu by pressing <<1>>, selecting Social, Guilds, and choose Browse Guilds.

The Guild Blacklist allows player guilds to flag a given account as being ineligible to join the associated guild. Accounts on the Blacklist cannot apply to or join that guild. 

Members with the Manage Blacklist permission can choose to add accounts to the blacklist when denying applications, removing members from the guild, or directly through the Blacklist menu. 

To access the Blacklist, open the Main Menu by pressing <<1>>, selecting Social, Guilds, followed by choosing a guild in which you have the Manage Blacklist permission, Recruitment, and Blacklist.

|t64:64:EsoUI/Art/Icons/Ability_Artifact_Volendrung_004.dds|t  |cFFFFFFAccursed Charge|r : Spring across the battlefield to smash an enemy, dealing 8000 Physical Damage.

Spending Points:
Once inside the preferred Minor Constellation, points can be allocated in the skills by using <<1>> <<2>>.

Each point spent in a Minor Constellation increases its rank. Once the Minor Constellation reaches a specific rank, passive abilities unlock for your character. If you respec your character, all passive abilities gained via rank in a specific Minor Constellation are lost until the appropriate number of points are reinvested.

Using <<1>> and <<2>> you can cycle through options for dyeing your armor.

|cFFFFFFDye|r allows you to dye a specific channel on a specific piece of armor.
|cFFFFFFDye All|r allows you to dye the same channel across all your pieces of armor.
|cFFFFFFClear Color|r allows you to clear a dye from a specific channel on a piece of armor. 
|cFFFFFFCopy Color|r allows you to copy the dye applied to a specific channel on a piece of armor.  

Note: Dyeing a piece of armor binds it to your account.

You may hire a Guild Trader at a Guild Trader station if no other guild has purchased their services. If another guild owns the services of a Guild Trader you may place a blind bid to try to acquire them when they become available.

Bidding occurs throughout the week, but players may only bid on one Trader per cycle. If you acquire the services of a Trader through bidding, their services will be yours for one week's time. 

Remember: You must continue bidding on a Trader to retain their services.

Soul Gems capture and store the souls of slain enemies. A filled Soul Gem can be used to charge magic weapons, revive a fallen ally, or revive yourself.

Empty Soul Gems
Find Soul Gems while adventuring or buy Soul Gems from Mystics, usually found at Mages Guild locations. Each type of Soul Gem can charge magic weapons or revive allies in a certain level range.

Filling Empty Soul Gems
Use the Soul Trap ability moments before an enemy's death. You cannot Soul Trap an enemy outside a Soul Gem's level range.

When your character is slain by another player in Cyrodiil, you can revive at any of your alliance's keeps that aren't currently under attack, or at a nearby forward camp. Your equipment will not suffer any durability loss.

Remember that other players can revive you using full Soul Gems. If you are slain and other players are nearby, you may want to wait for someone to revive you.

Source: Maelstrom Arena is a single-player progressive challenge located in the northeastern mountains of Wrothgar. Once discovered, you can use the fast travel network to return by selecting the Maelstrom Arena icon.\n\nThere are two difficulty modes available for Maelstrom Arena: Normal and Veteran. Players of any level can access Normal mode. Veteran mode unlocks when you reach level 50.  Veteran mode is much more challenging, but has greater rewards to match the risk!

Source: Guild relationships are formed at the player level, not the character level. When a player joins a guild, all of their characters will gain access to that guild regardless of their alliance affiliation.  Like your characters, guilds do have alliance affiliations. This distinction is important when the guild joins a campaign in the Alliance War. A guild can only claim a keep for its affiliated alliance.\n\nEach player can join up to 5 guilds, but a single player can only lead one guild at a time.
Target: Guild relationship은 캐릭터 레벨이 아니라 플레이어 레벨로 결정됩니다. 플레이어가 길드에 들어오면 플레이어의 모든 캐릭터는 연합 소속과 상관없이 길드의 권한을 가집니다. 다른 캐릭터처럼, 길드도 연합 소속을 가지고 있습니다. 이 점은 길드가 연합 전쟁에서 캠페인에 가입할 때 중요합니다. 한 길드는 소속된 연합의 요새만 요구할 수 있습니다.\n\n각 플레이어는 길드를 다섯 개까지 가입할 수 있지만 한 명의 플레이어는 한 번에 하나의 길드장만 될 수 있습니다.

Source: Elder Scrolls are of prime strategic importance to every alliance. Holding Elder Scrolls at a scroll temple or on a keep's scroll pedestal bestows special bonuses to every player of that alliance.
Target: 엘더 스크롤은 모든 연합에게 최고의 전략 자원입니다. scroll temple이나 요새의 스크롤 받침대에 엘더 스크롤을 보유하고 있으면 그 연합의 모든 플레이어에게 특별한 보너스를 제공합니다.

Source: Keep walls, keep doors, and siege weapons can all be repaired with the proper repair kit. To repair an object, target it and use the repair kit from a quickslot.\n\nYou cannot repair a keep wall if it has taken damage recently.
Target: 요새의 성벽과 성문, 그리고 공성 무기들은 적합한 수리 키트로 수리할 수 있습니다. 수리하려면 해당 오브젝트를 선택해서 퀵 슬롯에서 수리 키트를 사용하십시오.\n\n요새 성벽이 최근에 받은 데미지가 있다면 수리할 수 없습니다.

Source: To create a guild, open the Guild Menu by pressing the <<1>>   key. Then press the <<2>> key to begin creating a guild. You will need to give your guild a unique name and choose its alliance affiliation, then select "Create" to create your guild.

Source: Guild Chat is initiated through the chat line by typing "/g1" through "/g5". The number 1 through 5 indicates the corresponding number of the guild you wish to chat with. For example, typing "/g2 hey everyone" will change your chat channel to that of the second guild on your list, and then send the message "hey everyone" to that channel.

Source: To capture a resource, eliminate enough foes that your allies outnumber them near the flag.\n\nKeeps have two flags that must be turned to your alliance before the keep is captured.
Target: 자원을 확보하기 위해서는, 깃발 근처에서 아군이 적의 수를 능가할만큼 적을 충분히 처치하십시오.\n\n요새는 요새를 빼앗기기 전에 연합의 것으로 전환해야하는 두개의 깃발을 가집니다.

Source: Transitus Shrines provide fast travel routes between keeps, gates, and outposts, provided there is an unbroken link between where you are and where you want to go. Valid links and destinations glow brightly on your map.
Target: 당신이 있는 곳과 가기를 원하는 곳 사이에 끊기지 않은 링크가 있다면, 흐름(통행)의 성소는 요새, 관문, 전초 기지로의 빠른 여행을 제공합니다. 유효한 링크와 목적지는 지도에서 밝게 빛납니다.

Source: Forward camps provide an additional revival point for allied players who die in the immediate area. They are placed like siege weapons, but cannot be placed near another forward camp. Forward camps have a limited number of total revivals, and players cannot revive at a forward camp if they have recently revived at one.\n\nForward camps can be purchased from siege merchants with Alliance Points, provided you are Alliance Rank 6 or greater.
Target: 전초 기지는 인접 지역에서 죽은 아군 플레이어에게 추가적인 부활 포인트를 제공합니다. 전초 기지는 공성무기처럼 배치될 수 있지만 다른 전초 기지에서는 배치할 수 없습니다. 전초 기지는 부활시킬 수 있는 숫자가 제한되어 있으며 최근에 전초 기지에서 부활한 플레이어는 전초 기지에서 부활할 수 없습니다.\n\n연합 랭크가 6 이상이라면 연합 포인트를 사용하여 공성 상인에게서 전초 기지를 구입할 수 있습니다.

Source: Rams can be used to smash the main door of a keep, but they cannot be used on a keep's postern (side) doors. Rams can be deployed only near keeps.
Target: 공성추는 요새 정문을 공격하는 데 사용할 수 있지만, 요새의 뒷문(옆문)을 공격하는 데는 사용할 수 없습니다. 공성추는 인접한 요새 근처에만 배치할 수 있습니다.

Source:
When your character is slain by another player in Cyrodiil, you can revive at any of your alliance's keeps that aren't currently under attack, or at a nearby forward camp. Your equipment will not suffer any durability loss.

If you are slain, click on "Respawn" to see all of the available locations where you can revive.

Remember that other players can revive you using full Soul Gems. If you are slain and other players are nearby, you may want to wait for someone to revive you.

Source:
The Alliance War enables you to earn Alliance Points (APs) by aiding your side in battle. Killing enemy players and capturing or defending keeps and resource sites are some of the ways players can earn APs. 

APs can be used to purchase gear, siege equipment, repair kits, and more from your alliance's merchants in Cyrodiil.

APs increase your rank within your alliance.
Target:
연합 전쟁에서 진형에 속해 전투를 지원하여 연합 점수 (AP)를 벌어들일 수 있습니다. 플레이어는 AP를 적 플레이어를 죽이거나 사로잡고 요새나 자원 위치를 지켜 벌어들입니다.

AP는 시로딜에 있는 연합의 상인에게 장비나 공성 무기, 수리 키트 등을 사는데 사용할 수 있습니다.

AP는 당신의 연합 내 등급을 올려줍니다.

Source: The three alliances of Tamriel are at war with each other. To travel to Cyrodiil and participate in the Alliance War, you must be at least level 10.
Target: 탐리엘의 세 연합들은 각각 서로 전쟁을 하고 있습니다. 시로딜로 여행하고 연합 전쟁에 참여하기 위해서는 최소한 레벨 10에 도달해야 합니다.
